                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">Early birds ran with Dromo from Bello Puerto at sunrise, while the rest rolled in throughout the day. We posted up at Casa Pancha, explored the neighborhood (Condesa, Roma Norte), wandered Chapultepec, and grabbed tacos from local favorites.</p>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">That evening, we met as a full group for a 6K social run with Midnight Runners, followed by dinner and drinks at Chinampita Condesa.</p>
                    </div>
