                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full lg:w-6/12">
                        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white font-black uppercase my-2">Saturday</h3>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">Some got in an early morning shakeout in Chapultepec before our full-day excursion with Casa Pancha to the pyramids — a mix of running, history, and tacos outside the city. <span class="italic">Shout out to Alejandro for being the best guide.</span></p>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">Back in CDMX, we showered, grabbed a quick bite, then watched the Lions playoff game over wings and beers at Criminal Wings Condesa.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-y-8 mb-10 md:mb-20 justify-between items-center">
