                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full lg:w-6/12">
                        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white font-black uppercase my-2">Sunday</h3>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">We started the morning running down Paseo de la Reforma, which closes to traffic on Sundays — letting us join hundreds of runners and cyclists cruising the empty streets.</p>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">Later, we split up: some explored markets, downtown, or the zoo, while others got tattoos from local artists Mariano and Erika in a cozy, light-filled studio. We laughed, danced, and hung out while friends got inked — one of the most memorable moments of the trip.</p>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light">That evening, we came back together for dinner at <a href="https://app.pizzafelix.adomicil.io/" target="_blank">Pizza Felix</a>.</p>
